Parliament, Monday, 21 January 2019 – The Ad Hoc Committee to identify suitable candidates for the filling of vacancies at the Commission for Gender Equality (CGE)will tomorrow meet to be briefed and updated on progress made with regards to filling of vacancies. Details of the meeting: Date: Tuesday, 22 January 2019
	Time: 10:00 – 18:00
	Venue: V475, Old Assembly Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES ON BEHALF OF THE CHAIRPERSON OF THE AD HOC COMMITTEE TO IDENTIFY SUITABLE CANDIDATES FOR THE FILLING OF VACANCIES AT THE COMMISSION FOR GENDER EQUALITY, MS NONHLANHLA NCUBE-NDABA. For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Yoliswa Landu
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8203 
	Cell: 081 497 4694
